1. Install Anaconda (URL: https://www.continuum.io/downloads)
 - or
	- Install Python (URL: https://www.python.org/downloads)

2. Update PyPA
	pip install --upgrade pip

3. Install packages
 - from Anaconda
	conda install numpy scipy pandas matplotlib seaborn statsmodels scikit-learn pydot
 - from PyPA
	pip install numpy scipy pandas matplotlib seaborn statsmodels scikit-learn pydot

4. Update packages
 - from Anaconda
	conda update numpy scipy pandas matplotlib seaborn statsmodels scikit-learn pydot
 - from PyPA
	pip install --upgrade numpy scipy pandas matplotlib seaborn statsmodels scikit-learn pydot
